      <title>南非旅游胜地遭遇暴雨和强风袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/cape-town-south-africa-s-tourism-mecca-hit-by-torrential-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非旅游之都开普敦遭受暴雨和狂风袭击，基础设施遭到严重破坏，数千名贫民窟居民被迫撤离家园。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/cape-town-south-africa-s-tourism-mecca-hit-by-torrential-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:25:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛克称美联储不会在 7 月份降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/the-fed-won-t-cut-rates-in-july-slok-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗首席经济学家托尔斯滕·斯洛克表示，美联储不会在 7 月份降息。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/the-fed-won-t-cut-rates-in-july-slok-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
